{
  "id": "RAW_de1ae8",
  "title": "Gemini 中的图像编辑迎来重大升级",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/discover/blog/image-editing-in-gemini-just-got-a-major-upgrade/",
  "date": "2025-08-26 15:40:29",
  "author": "David Sharon",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-08-26T15:40:29.092952+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"cdud0\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today in the <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini app</a>, we're unveiling a new image editing model from Google DeepMind. People have been going <i>bananas</i> over it already in early previews — it's the <a href=\"https://lmarena.ai/leaderboard/image-edit\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">top-rated</a> image editing model in the world. Now, we're excited to share that it's integrated into the Gemini app so you have more control than ever to create the perfect picture.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"7uh8n\">Maintain your look as you edit</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"4f8ie\"><a href=\"http://blog.google/products/gemini/image-editing\">We launched native image editing</a> in the Gemini app earlier this year, and we’ve been working hard to improve it, with particular focus on maintaining a character's likeness from one image to the next. We know that when editing pictures of yourself or people you know well, subtle flaws matter — a depiction that’s \"close but not quite the same\" doesn’t feel right. That's why our latest update is designed to make photos of your friends, family and even your pets look consistently like themselves, whether you're trying out a 60’s beehive haircut or putting a tutu on your chihuahua.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9l027\">Just give Gemini a photo to work with, and tell it what you'd like to change to add your unique touch. Gemini lets you combine photos to put yourself in a picture with your pet, change the background of a room to preview new wallpaper or place yourself anywhere in the world you can imagine — all while keeping you, you. Once you're done, you can even upload your edited image back into Gemini to turn your new photo into a fun video.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"7pu0r\">Bring your vision to life with advanced editing</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2irgr\">Here are a few things to try as you explore this new image editing capability:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"3an76\"><b>Give yourself a costume or location change</b>: Upload a photo of a person or pet, and our model will keep their look the same in every image as you place them in new scenarios. Try putting yourself in different outfits or professions, or even see how you’d appear in another decade — all while still looking like you.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app turning a blonde woman's photo into a picture of her as a bullfighter, artist, and '90s styled persona\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Character consistency\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Character_consistency_TR7mVxk.mp4\" section-header=\"Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app turning a blonde woman's photo into a picture of her as a bullfighter, artist, and '90s styled persona\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Character_consistency_TR7mVxk.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Character_consistency_TR7mVxk.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"vqjvg\"><b>Blend photos together</b>: You can now upload multiple photos and blend them together for a brand-new scene. For example, take your photo and another of your dog to create a perfect portrait of you both on the basketball court.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app blending a picture of a woman and a picture of a dog to show the woman and dog together on a basketball court\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Blend photos together\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Blend_photos_together_w8GsoJi.mp4\" section-header=\"Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app blending a picture of a woman and a picture of a dog to show the woman and dog together on a basketball court\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Blend_photos_together_w8GsoJi.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Blend_photos_together_w8GsoJi.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"mq3v4\"><b>Try multi-turn editing</b>: You can keep editing the images Gemini makes — take an empty room, paint the walls, then add a bookshelf, some furniture or a coffee table. Gemini's working with you all along to alter specific parts of an image while preserving the rest.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app decorating a room by adding salmon walls, bookshelves, a green velvet sofa and a Persian rug\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"ImageEditing\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/ImageEditingGemini_Inline_XZuiDzE.mp4\" section-header=\"Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app decorating a room by adding salmon walls, bookshelves, a green velvet sofa and a Persian rug\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/ImageEditingGemini_Inline_XZuiDzE.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/ImageEditingGemini_Inline_XZuiDzE.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"mq3v4\"><b>Mix up designs</b>: Apply the style of one image to an object in another. You can take the color and texture of flower petals and apply it to a pair of rainboots, or design a dress using the pattern from a butterfly's wings.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app applying styles from one photo, like a pink flower, to another photo, like blue rainboots\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Design mixing\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Design_mixing_fJ8ZjJA.mp4\" section-header=\"Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"GIF showing native image editing in the Gemini app applying styles from one photo, like a pink flower, to another photo, like blue rainboots\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Design_mixing_fJ8ZjJA.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Design_mixing_fJ8ZjJA.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?lit$598423377$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Image editing in Gemini just got a major upgrade&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"mq3v4\">You can try this updated image editing capability in the Gemini app starting today. All images created or edited in the Gemini app include a visible watermark, as well as our invisible SynthID digital watermark, to clearly show they are AI-generated.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 新的图像编辑模型已集成到 Gemini 应用中，提供高级功能，如角色一致性、多轮编辑和照片混合，从而实现顶级性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 新的图像编辑模型已集成到 Gemini 应用中，提供高级功能，如角色一致性、多轮编辑和照片混合，从而实现顶级性能。",
  "summary": "本文宣布了 Gemini 应用中图像编辑功能的重大升级，该功能由 Google DeepMind 的新型模型提供支持。该模型被誉为世界顶级的图像编辑模型，现在为用户提供了前所未有的创造性控制，以创作完美的图片。重点介绍的关键功能包括在编辑过程中保持角色相似性（例如，对于人或宠物）、将多张照片混合到新的场景中（例如，将您自己和您的宠物放在篮球场上），以及先进的多轮编辑，允许迭代修改，同时保留其他图像部分（例如，粉刷墙壁然后添加家具）。它还引入了混合设计的能力，通过将一种图像的风格应用于另一种图像中的对象，例如在雨靴上使用花瓣纹理。这些功能旨在帮助用户更轻松地将他们的创造性愿景变为现实，所有 AI 生成或编辑的图像都包含可见和不可见的 (SynthID) 水印。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Gemini 的新图像编辑模型因其先进的功能而在全球范围内名列前茅。",
      "explanation": "该模型已集成到 Gemini 应用中，在图像编辑方面实现了最先进的性能，为用户提供了强大的创意控制工具。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型擅长在各种编辑和场景中保持角色相似性。",
      "explanation": "此次更新的核心重点是确保个人或宠物的一致描绘，这对于逼真和个性化的图像修改至关重要。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多轮编辑和照片混合等高级功能增强了创造性可能性。",
      "explanation": "用户可以迭代地优化图像并组合来自多张照片的元素，从而在实现他们的愿景方面提供前所未有的灵活性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "人们已经在早期预览中对它感到*疯狂*——它是世界上评价最高的图像编辑模型。",
    "我们的最新更新旨在让您的朋友、家人甚至宠物的照片始终如一地像他们自己，无论您是想尝试 60 年代的蜂窝发型还是给您的吉娃娃穿上芭蕾舞裙。",
    "Gemini 一直在与您合作，以改变图像的特定部分，同时保留其余部分。"
  ],
